// error-002-multiple-arms.scrml
// Error effect with multiple match arms. Tests: !{} with several patterns.

<div>
    !{
        | ::NotFoundError e -> let status = 404
        | ::AuthError e -> let status = 401
        | ::ServerError e -> let status = 500
        | _ e -> let status = 0
    }
    <p>Multi-error handler</>
</div>
